{"tid":829650,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[潮店回歸] Foot Locker回歸開三層大舖 首天排隊安排惹鞋迷不滿","createTime":"2018-09-20T15:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T16:18:55.000Z","uid":104793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0e12cdb24b9849049b6338d0101482d56d304a31","tid":829650,"uid":104793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T15:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180920/large/1537437352_a439.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180920%2Flarge%2F1537437352_a439.jpg&h=48f4a3a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你係80後或更年長的鞋迷，一定知道Foot Locker曾經也在香港大展拳腳，但後來隨波鞋熱轉淡，就撤出了香港。不過近年波鞋潮流重生，呢間喺歐美都大把分店的知名波鞋連鎖店，終於回歸，喺尖沙咀開設3層巨舖，更同時帶來出名多特別款籃球鞋的附屬店「HOUSE OF HOOPS」。新店正式開張，作為鞋迷的記者當然要去潮一潮聖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新店坐落九龍公園徑1號，單看外型已夠晒霸氣，外牆設計非常有特色，隔幾條街都見到。內裏裝修亦富特色，大大個locker用嚟暫存客人留起的貨品，更有黑人駐場DJ打碟，加上一大班有型店員，整間舖的氣氛都跟香港一般波鞋舖有所不同，更富外國潮味。當然喇，貨品才是主打，店內基本有齊各大品牌的潮鞋，種類頗多，記者更發現BB和童裝鞋比一般店舖多，潮媽潮爸唔好走漏眼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180920/small/1537437363_1bcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180920%2Fsmall%2F1537437363_1bcd.jpg&h=3a376eed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180920/58704561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180920%2F58704561&d=VUUc2fuwnPA%2FjAcv7wt5Zm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=3f2b38b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180920%2F58704561&h=67c648d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180920/58704561</a>"},{"pid":"7ff858b81a359b23eec8e7b3487ac3f3d24d8837","tid":829650,"uid":7823,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"最緊要 齊款巴黎世家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4a656b033170041d63e5e38311b43234e3d552","tid":829650,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T15:57:00.000Z","msg":"完全接收esprit facade 慳唔少錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7356f832a06e9b2e17e6f6f13fc43357883aa32","tid":829650,"uid":124741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:16:23.000Z","msg":"圍唔圍到皮...."},{"pid":"7ad4f3ea42e268420b4ee8f61580c39c6477a6a2","tid":829650,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7356f832a06e9b2e17e6f6f13fc43357883aa32","tid":829650,"uid":124741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:16:23.000Z","msg":"圍唔圍到皮...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:18:55.000Z","msg":"搞手打個和"}]}